OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FThe trial of a former paratrooper
OL,7,Faccused of murdering two men in
OL,8,FLondonderry more than 50 years ago has
OL,9,Fheard an eye witness account of
OL,10,F"pandemonium" with people screaming
OL,11,Fand shots being fired.
OL,13,FThe statement of Bloody Sunday eye
OL,14,Fwitness Jon McCourt also recounted
OL,15,Fbeing shot by a rubber bullet by a
OL,16,Fsoldier himself, despite not posing
OL,17,Fany threat.
