OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FSoldier F, who cannot be named for
OL,7,Flegal reasons, is accused of the
OL,8,Fmurders of James Wray and William
OL,9,FMcKinney.
OL,11,FThey were among 13 people shot dead by
OL,12,Fthe Parachute Regiment at a civil
OL,13,Frights demonstration in the Bogside
OL,14,Farea of Londonderry on January 30 1972.
OL,16,FThe Army veteran is also accused of
OL,17,Fattempting to murder Michael Quinn,
OL,18,FPatrick O'Donnell, Joseph Friel, Joe
OL,19,FMahon and an unknown person.
