OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FHe has pleaded not guilty to the seven
OL,7,Fcounts.
OL,9,FSoldier F sits in the courtroom at
OL,10,FBelfast Crown Court behind a curtain
OL,11,Fduring each day of the trial which
OL,12,Fbegan last month.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday morning the court heard
OL,15,Fstatements from witnesses read out.
OL,17,FThese included the account of retired
OL,18,Fengineer Jon McCourt, who recalled
OL,19,Fchaotic scenes in the Glenfada Park
OL,20,Farea, and previously gave evidence to
OL,21,Fthe Saville Inquiry.
