OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FHe said he had been attending a family
OL,7,Ffuneral on the morning of the
OL,8,Fshootings at Derry City Cemetery, and
OL,9,Fupon leaving joined the civil rights
OL,10,Fmarch as it proceeded along Westland
OL,11,FStreet.
OL,13,FHowever, after they heard of a
OL,14,Fpotential confrontation he said he
OL,15,Ftold his wife and in-law relations to
OL,16,Fgo to another relative's house at
OL,17,FGlenfada Park North.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
