OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FHe said he went on himself and saw
OL,7,Frioters throw stones at soldiers, and
OL,8,Falso saw mist and smoke in the air
OL,9,Ffrom CS gas, as well as hearing bangs.
OL,11,FIntending to join his family, he
OL,12,Fdescribed getting caught up with those
OL,13,Ffleeing shootings at Glenfada Park,
OL,14,Fand got shot with a rubber bullet by a
OL,15,Fsoldier.
OL,17,F"He aimed in my direction with a
OL,18,Frubber bullet gun, which he held at
OL,19,Fshoulder height. He was alone. The
OL,20,Fsoldier was wearing a black beret.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
