OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,F"He fired and I was hit in the left
OL,7,Fthigh by a rubber bullet, I believe
OL,8,Fthe bullet may have ricocheted before
OL,9,Fit hit me because I did not feel too
OL,10,Fmuch pain when I was hit ` if it had
OL,11,Fbeen a direct hit I do not think I'd
OL,12,Fhave been able to walk, much less
OL,13,Frun," he said.
OL,15,F"I was not holding or throwing a
OL,16,Fstone, I was not threatening him in
OL,17,Fany way and I did nothing to justify
OL,18,Fbeing shot at."
