OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FMr McCourt said he then headed to his
OL,7,Fwife's relations' house, and described
OL,8,Fseeing "pandemonium" in the square.
OL,10,F"There was a lot of noise from people
OL,11,Fsquealing and screaming ... I could
OL,12,Fhear shots that seemed to come from
OL,13,Fall directions," he said.
OL,15,F"I did not actually see anyone firing
OL,16,Fthe shots, the shots came from behind
OL,17,Fme as I was running towards my wife's
OL,18,Fgrandmother's house.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@TO]rD@AOUuD@PO]wD@AOU
