OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,F"It was single shots with a gap
OL,7,Fbetween them. The shots were live
OL,8,Fammunition ` they were not rubber
OL,9,Fbullets, a rubber bullet makes a
OL,10,Fdifferent sound.
OL,12,F"The panic in Glenfada Park North
OL,13,Fcontinued ... I heard people shouting,
OL,14,F'don't shoot', 'lie down', 'get out of
OL,15,Fmy way'.
OL,17,F"I noticed a young fella, about 14 or
OL,18,F15 years of age in hysterics close to
OL,19,Fme, I pulled him in with me and told
OL,20,Fhim to stay down."
