OL,3,C'People were screaming': Bloody Sunday
OL,4,Cwitness describes 'pandemonium'
OL,6,FMr McCourt also recalled shouting to
OL,7,Fpeople nearby to keep still and not
OL,8,Fmove, but did not hear any response.
OL,10,F"I would be certain they would have
OL,11,Fheard me as they were very close to
OL,12,Fwhere I was, and I was shouting.
OL,14,F"I believe that Jim Wray, who was
OL,15,Fkilled that day, would have been among
OL,16,Fthe group of people I was calling to,
OL,17,Fthese people who were lying there.
OL,19,F"I didn't know at the time whether
OL,20,Fthey were wounded or simply lying
OL,21,Fthere, or dead, or what."
